<h2 class="md mb-4 mt-14 md:mt-20 text-grey6 font-sans-heading text-hS md:text-hL font-bold uppercase max-w-[793px] mx-auto">Design system</h2>
<h3 class="md mb-[0.875rem] md:mb-4 mt-8 md:mt-10 text-grey6 font-sans-heading text-hS md:text-hM max-w-[793px] mx-auto">About project</h3>
<p class="md mb-[0.875rem] max-w-[793px] mx-auto">MYRIG Design System is developed on the principles of Atomic design, starting from the base simplest elements and creating together more complex components, templates and pages.</p>
